alert.note: Alert for San Luis Obispo County Mountains; Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Watch issued April 01 at 3:12AM PDT until April 04 at 5:00AM PDT by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WATCH IN EFFECT FROM LATE SUNDAY NIGHT THROUGH LATE MONDAY NIGHT... * WHAT...Northwest winds 35 to 45 mph with gusts 60 to 65 mph possible. * WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Mountains and Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains. * WHEN...From late Sunday night through late Monday night. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds could blow down large objects such as trees and power lines. Power outages are possible. Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe location prior to the onset of winds.
